  "abstract": "This report illustrates our commitment to this endeavor and showcases some of the stories of women\r\nwe are working with in the region. Even more than showing what we have achieved, it serves to\r\nhighlight how much more needs to be done to ensure that we develop a systematic research approach\r\nto guarantee women’s participation, empowerment and advancement through agriculture.",
